.Ss AVATAR-SPECIFIC OPTIONS
.Pp
.Bl -tag -width "--concatenate" -compact
.It Fl -include Ar range
.It Fl -exclude Ar range
Include or exclude the one-based column indices in 
.Ar range .
.Fl -include
and
.Fl -exclude
may be specified together and may each be specified multiple times. They
are applied left to right.
.It Fl -truth-column Ar num
The one-based column index in the data file which corresponds to the true class for each sample.
The default is the last column in the file.
.El
